trending.title: Trending Now
trending.description: The movies and shows Tubi lovers are buzzing about right now.

8076.title: White Zombie
8076.description: When a wealthy plantation owner becomes obsessed with a beautiful but unattainable woman, he strikes a devil's bargain with a sinister voodoo master!

11484.title: Keoma

663265.title: My Friend Dahmer (Broadcast Edit)
663265.description: The true story of Jeffrey Dahmer in high school before he became one of America's most infamous serial killers. Based on the acclaimed graphic novel.

664045.title: Dark Night of the Scarecrow
664045.description: After finding young Marylee Williams mauled viciously, bigots pursue as a suspect her intellectually disabled friend Bubba Ritter.

664742.title: Speed
664742.description: A city bus with a bomb aboard is set to explode if it falls under 50 mph. An L.A. officer must help one of the passengers steer the bus to safety.

666100.title: The Bear
666100.description: Follows the story of a young orphan cub and an adult grizzly as they join forces to survive being hunted down by humans in their mountain habitat.

666459.title: Open Graves
666459.description: Jason and his surfer friends begin playing an old board game called Mamba. They soon discover that the game claims a life every time it is played.

669934.title: The Black Room
669934.description: The Hemdales move into their dream house, but their happy marriage is put to the test when they discover that something is living in the cellar.

672228.title: The Recall
672228.description: When five friends vacation at a remote lake house, they are unaware that planet Earth is under an alien invasion and mass-abduction.

674393.title: Convoy
674393.description: Martin, in pursuance of a feud with a sheriff, unites scores of his fellow drivers into a convoy, rolling towards the freedom of the Mexican border.

676681.title: The Moth Diaries
676681.description: An innocent teen is drawn into a darkly erotic world after enrolling at an elite boarding school and befriending the secretive girl across the hall.

679301.title: The Great Buck Howard
679301.description: When his career performs a vanishing act, a pompous magician hires a law school drop-out and a fiery publicist to help him stage a dazzling comeback.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

681749.title: The Unknown Girl
681749.description: After a mysterious young woman dies on her doorstep, a guilt-ridden doctor embarks on an obsessive quest to learn the truth about what happened.

681755.title: Pelé: Birth of a Legend
681755.description: Regarded as one of the greatest sports heroes ever, Pelé, a kid from the slums of Brazil, transformed soccer into the world's biggest sport.

684142.title: Evolution
684142.description: On a remote island where young boys are subjected to strange medical treatments, one boy makes a disturbing discovery beneath the waves.

684358.title: Cuck
684358.description: A lonely and isolated young man gains popularity as an online Alt-Right vlogger, which feeds his fevered zealotry to a bloody end.

685748.title: The Standoff at Sparrow Creek
685748.description: A reclusive ex-cop finds himself forced out of retirement when he realizes that a killer belongs to the same militia he joined after the force.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

693355.title: Bloodsucking Freaks
693355.description: In New York's Theatre of the Macabre, Sardu and his assistants present a show inflicting real torture, mutilation and death upon unwilling subjects.

703583.title: Apocalipsis Zombie (Doblado)
703583.description: Un escuadrón de fuerzas especiales se infiltra en una zona de cuarentena para rescatar a un científico que tiene la cura para salvar a la humanidad.

711708.title: The Hole in the Ground
711708.description: A woman suspects that her son, who returned home after disappearing in the woods, is an imposter.

711709.title: American Honey
711709.description: An adolescent girl from a troubled home runs away with a traveling sales crew who drive across the American Midwest selling subscriptions door to door.

713110.title: The Mercenary
713110.description: While pursued by a U.S. rival, a greedy Polish mercenary aids a mine worker and peasant girl as they lead a revolution against the Mexican government.

723734.title: Antibirth
723734.description: Two friends get caught up in a government conspiracy when they awaken after a wild night of drug-fueled partying with a strange illness and visions.

724374.title: Big Fan
724374.description: A parking garage attendant, who lives for New York Giants football, struggles to deal with the fallout when he gets beaten up by his favorite player.

724568.title: A Case of You
724568.description: After meeting a charming woman, a young writer stalks her internet profile to become the kind of man who embodies all of her interests.

725088.title: Jimmy P: Psychotherapy of a Plains Indian
725088.description: A Blackfoot Indian whose skull was fractured in World War II forms a bond with a bold French psychoanalyst trying to cure his emotional battle scars.

725363.title: House on Willow Street
725363.description: Kidnapped and held for the ransom of her jeweler father’s fortune in diamonds, a young woman with a dark secret finds an upper hand with her captors.

100000179.title: The Tall Man
100000179.description: A nurse in a dying mining town dismisses the rumors about disappearing local children until her own son vanishes in the middle of the night.

100000690.title: Liberal Arts
100000690.description: A comical coming-of-age story about an unlikely romance between a jaded 35-year-old college counselor and a precocious 19-year-old student.

100000954.title: Pledge
100000954.description: A group of college freshmen pledges an exclusive fraternity. But they soon realize there's more at stake than they could have imagined.

100001720.title: Man Up
100001720.description: Disillusioned by her pathetic love life, a single woman poses as a stranger’s blind date and inadvertently finds the perfect boyfriend.

0300005291.title: Danger 5
0300005291.description: Set in a dystopian version of the year 1982, five spies set out to kill Adolf Hitler before he kills them to achieve world domination by Christmas.

04604.title: The Titanic
04604.description: Follow stories of romance and adventure as passengers settle aboard the doomed ship, brought to life in this dramatic and intense miniseries.

02377.title: Full Metal Panic? Fumoffu
02377.description: Sousuke’s a great soldier, but he’s an awkward classmate and Kaname knows that better than anyone, since he is undercover as her bodyguard at school.

03851.title: Human Trafficking
03851.description: US Immigration and Customs Enforcement agents go undercover to battle an organized crime ring and help the women who have been victimized.

0300006585.title: Dancing on the Edge
0300006585.description: In 1930s London, a black jazz group wins favor with aristocrats, but fame brings tragedy, as they get entangled in elite society’s web of intrigue.

04512.title: 5ive Days to Midnight
04512.description: With only five days to left live, a university professor must answer the questions that haunt his last few sleepless nights: Who wants him dead and why?

02269.title: Eden of the East
02269.description: Akira Takizawa wakes up outside the White House with a phone that gives him access to ten billion yen and a woman who will grant any request. He doesn’t remember he’s supposed to save Japan. And he doesn’t remember that he’ll be killed if he fails.

0300005163.title: The Masked Singer
0300005163.description: Celebrity performers, costumed to conceal their identities but dropping hints along the way, compete each week as one is eliminated and unmasked.
